00:06:30.060 --> 00:06:33.000
But the computer kept on
getting more interesting.

00:06:33.000 --> 00:06:34.590
It came out of prints.

00:06:34.590 --> 00:06:35.970
It became interactive.

00:06:35.970 --> 00:06:38.830
Who remembers
Macromedia Director?

00:06:38.830 --> 00:06:39.420
Macro mind.

00:06:39.420 --> 00:06:39.990
